\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The Independent Institute of Education \'28IIE\'29 is a private higher education institution that is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training and has programmes that are accredited by the CHE. \line \line The Institution is currently applying for the accreditation of the Diploma in Journalism Studies programme which will be offered in the contact mode of delivery at the following sites\'3A\line 1. IIE Rosebank College\'2C Pretoria - Pretoria \line 2. IIE Rosebank College\'2C Braamfontein Mega - Braamfontein\'2C Johannesburg \line 3. IIE Rosebank College - Durban - Durban \line \line The Institution has the following programmes that are accredited in the field of Journalism\'3A \line - Diploma in Journalism Studies\line - Higher Certificate in Journalism\line \line The Institution has also applied for the accreditation of a Higher Certificate in Journalism programme to be offered in the contact mode of delivery.\cell \pard 

